Class FieldInfos

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.marketdata.FieldInfos
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFieldInfos
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FixFieldInfos

    public class FieldInfos
extends Object
implements IFieldInfos
    Standard implementation of IFieldInfos which provides the field names for all standard market data fields.
